{"type": "article", "id": 19796, "title": "宠物珍珠项链系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-28T07:40:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134711OM3tQ1JGu5bKg7TH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 nendo 为旗下的设计品牌 by | n 新出的宠物珍珠项链系列。他们设计了银制鸟笼、狗屋、猫垫和仓鼠的转轮，然后在中间放上珍珠，让人们能够联想到对应的小动物。银制的外框是精细复杂的，对比之下圆形的珍珠显得简单纯粹，也有更多的想象空间，正是一实一虚的关系，在日渐趋同的珠宝设计里独树一帜。他们另外设计了将珍珠镶嵌起来的戒指，<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/pet-pearl-collection-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150204o7FQbU1esRXImOWS.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"468\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150205wneBkr1Zz4LqWt9i.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150205ned6iF9Y0BWyEMDQ.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150206RyAJdvo0qTIgXCaN.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261502074Qqym072UoscwGRu.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}